            <h2>GET - Retrive documents</h2>
            <p>
                Get from UpCloo index is pretty simple, you have to do a simple
                HTTP get request specifing your <code>sitekey</code> and the 
                <code>id</code> of content. UpCloo replies with a document with
                a list of content correlates.
            </p>
            <p>
                <code>http://repository.upcloo.com/{sitekey}/{id}.xml</code>
            </p>
