            <p>
                If you have different <em>virtual sitekeys</em> you can retrive other
                correlation aspects using a sub key. For do this task simple send
                after the primary key. See an example: 
                <code>http://repository.upcloo.com/{sitekey}/{vsitekey}/{id}.xml</code>
            </p>
            <p>
                UpCloo firewalls limit get requests only to your dedicates ips.
                If you want you can skip firewalls and allows all to get your
                content correlations.
